  <p>Remember to <b>never copy anything</b> off of these websites. They are just here to give you an idea of what types of things to write about.</p>

  <p>A powerful strategy for choosing what to write about is to search for a broad category you're interested in writing about, then seeing what comes up. If you narrow your search and look at the "suggested" keywords in the search bar, you can get a sense of what people are searching for. If it's unique enough, you could generate lots of traffic through organic searches.</p>

